1. index
2. visited
3. map pointer
4. termininating and input validation [this is called base case handling]
5. recursion and backtracking

How to write recursion
1. Express everything in terms i and j
2. Explore all possibilities 
3. Explore base cases 
4. Return sum of all possibilities 

Backtracking 
1. take and not take
2. or a for loop and combination of take and not take , and comparing with the previous elements to see if you have picked it or not 